Web InterfaceEnvironment VariablesConfiguration File <ol> <li>Navigate to Settings</li> <li>Find Plex Integration section</li> <li>Enter Plex URL: <code>http://your-plex-server:32400</code></li> <li>Enter your Plex Token</li> <li>Click Save</li> </ol> <pre><code>PLEX_URL=http://your-plex-server:32400
PLEX_TOKEN=your-authentication-token
</code></pre> <pre><code>{
  "plex": {
    "url": "http://your-plex-server:32400",
    "token": "your-authentication-token"
  }
}
</code></pre>
